message.content: cs.LO, cs.LO is the most likely category as the paper deals with coalgebras on Stone spaces, which are closely related to the study of logic and set theory. Other likely categories could include cs.LT (formal languages and automata theory), cs.DM (discrete mathematics), cs.LG (machine learning), and cs.PL (programming languages), as the paper also deals with bisimulations and behavioural equivalence, which are important concepts in these areas.
